geom-gl
=======

Native OpenGL geometry & matrix library for jolt, ported from thi.ng/geom.

This product includes software developed as part of thi.ng/geom
(https://thi.ng/geom) by Karsten Schmidt, licensed under the Apache License,
Version 2.0. The matrix arithmetic, cofactor inversion, and constructor
formulas are derived from geom's thi.ng.geom.matrix.

geom-gl is licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0 (see ./LICENSE),
which is compatible with jolt's Eclipse Public License 1.0.
